data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom 3 full bath home in Pinnacle Estates! This home has room for everyone! Office upon entry that could be a 5th bedroom. Formal dining and large closet perfect for your serving dishes just outside dining area. Living area is light and bright with cozy fireplace and open to kitchen. Kitchen is a chefs delight with walk in pantry, large island, breakfast bar and eat in area. Primary suite is downstairs and is large and bath features soaking tub, separate shower, dual sinks and large walk in closet. One additional bed and bath downstairs could be perfect for multi generational living. Upstairs are two additional bedrooms and another full bath! This home is perfect for entertaining with a large lot size of .27 and a back patio perfect for grilling outdoors! Don't miss this home and it could be yours for the holidays!
